{"word":"γνύπετος","slug":"γνύπετος","sections":[{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":"<entryFree id=\"n22495\" key=\"gnu/petos\" type=\"main\" opt=\"n\" TEIform=\"entryFree\"> <orth extent=\"full\" lang=\"greek\" opt=\"n\" TEIform=\"orth\">γνύπετος</orth>, <itype lang=\"greek\" opt=\"n\" TEIform=\"itype\">ον</itype>, (<etym lang=\"greek\" opt=\"n\" TEIform=\"etym\">γόνυ, πίπτω</etym>) <sense id=\"n22495.0\" n=\"A\" level=\"1\" opt=\"n\" TEIform=\"sense\"> <tr_ opt=\"n\" TEIform=\"tr\">falling on the knee</tr_>:—hence <orth extent=\"full\" lang=\"greek\" opt=\"n\" TEIform=\"orth\">γνυπτέω</orth> (leg. <foreign lang=\"greek\" TEIform=\"foreign\">γνυπετέω</foreign>), <tr_ opt=\"n\" TEIform=\"tr\">to be weak</tr_>, <bibl default=\"NO\" TEIform=\"bibl\"> <author TEIform=\"author\"><a class=\"S\" href=\"S:LSJ Hsch.\">Hsch.</a></author> </bibl> <orth extent=\"full\" lang=\"greek\" opt=\"n\" TEIform=\"orth\">γνύποντι</orth> (leg. <foreign lang=\"greek\" TEIform=\"foreign\">-οῦντι</foreign>)<foreign lang=\"greek\" TEIform=\"foreign\">· ἀσθενοῦντι</foreign>, Id., and <orth extent=\"full\" lang=\"greek\" opt=\"n\" TEIform=\"orth\">γνύπων</orth>, <itype lang=\"greek\" opt=\"n\" TEIform=\"itype\">ωνος</itype>, <tr_ opt=\"n\" TEIform=\"tr\">depressed</tr_> or <tr_ opt=\"n\" TEIform=\"tr\">weak</tr_>, Id.</sense> </entryFree>"}]}